plify the model proposed in this\npaper, which make it possible for obtaining global optimal solution by using\nthe commercial software.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Mar 2018 07:32:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-21"}
